Archive gems from Dalston's Cafe OTO - championing creative new music that exists outside of the mainstream. Everything from free jazz to footwork, recorded and released via cafeoto.co.uk.
Recordings from the series are available via https://www.cafeoto.co.uk/shop/category/otoroku-downloads/.
